description:
An interactive tribute to the Cyber Gecko Gang project.
https://cybergeckogang.xyz


coded with <3 by ryxns

All background images should be scaled to 1920x1080

*Backgrounds can be updated more than once.*


To add your Gecko:
- First download the original image from IPFS
- Then remove the background color leaving a transparent background
(use photoshop etc) and save as transparent PNG (1080x1080).

*Geckos cannot be updated more than once. F5 to refresh.*
